<p>Table1</p>  <pre><code>Color, Total ------------ Red,5 Blue,3 Pink,1 </code></pre>  <p>Table2</p>  <pre><code>Color, Total ------------ Red,3 Blue,2 Pink,1 </code></pre>  <p>The desired result would be:</p>  <pre><code>Results Color, Total ------------ Red,2 Blue,1 Pink,0 </code></pre>  <p>How do I subtract total column in table2 from total column in table1?</p>  <p><a href="http://sqlfiddle.com/#!3/9eecb7db59d16c80417c72d1/2498" rel="nofollow">http://sqlfiddle.com/#!3/9eecb7db59d16c80417c72d1/2498</a></p>